des:
Experience luxury and get the most out of your Forest Shuttle system by controlling your curtains with Alexa. Open or close your curtains remotely (even when you are at work or on vacation) and discover very useful features of Alexa.
Use Alexa to set up and operate your Forest Shuttle and set up your favorite routines. With Alexa you launch your drapery into the world of the Internet Of Things, in which you can control your curtains by using your mobile device or by voice. 

Key features:
• Control your Forest Shuttle from anywhere
• Add and control multiple Forest Shuttle Systems 
• Control your curtains by voice
• Multiple routines or scenes can be set. Program your curtains so that they close when it gets dark outside that they open when it becomes light outside.
• Simply add and connect other smart devices within the App and control them via routines or scenes. For example: lighting and alarm systems.
• Easily and quickly connect to a Forest Shuttle System with WiFi dongle.

After connecting Alexa to your Forest Connect products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "Forest Connect" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one Forest Connect account in our " Forest Connect" app;
(3). You need to have some Forest Connect devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our "Forest Connect" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "Forest Connect" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "Forest Connect" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "Forest Connect", and you'll be navigated to Forest Connect login page;
(9). Input your Forest Connect account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
“Alexa,turn on the curtain.”
“Alexa,turn off the curtain.”
